<div class="sectionpages">
<p>At <span class="boldpage"> Allworld Corporation </span>, We are committed to our customers by delivering the highest quality mobile phones and electronic products that anticipate and satisfy people's needs and desires, while offering affordability and convenience.</p>
<p> for any reason you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, we offer a clear and fair return and refund process.</p><br>
<h3>1. General Return and Refund Conditions</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="boldpage"> Eligibility for Returns:</span> To be eligible for a return, the item must be in <span class="boldpage"> unused, unopened,</span> and <span class="boldpage">resalable condition </span> (in its original packaging, with all tags, and accessories). </li>
            <p> For defective or damaged items, returns are accepted within <span class="boldpage">7 days </span> from the date you receive the item. </p>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Return Period:</span> You have <span class="boldpage"> 7 days </span> from the date of delivery to request a return or exchange.</li><br>
        <li><span class="boldpage"> Non-returnable Items: </span> Certain items are non-returnable, including: </li>
            <ul style="list-style-type:circle;">
                <li>Gadgets that have been <span class="boldpage">opened, used,</span> or <span class="boldpage">tampered</span> with</li>
                <li>Software, digital products, or gift cards</li>
                <li>Items that are customized or personalized</li>
            </ul>
    </ul>
<h3>2. How to Return an Item</h3>
<p>If you wish to return an item, follow these steps:</p>
    <ol>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Contact Us:</span> Reach out to our customer support team at <span class="boldpage">customercare@allworld.info or +63 966 891 1848 </span> within 7 days of receiving the item to initiate your return.</li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Provide Order Information:</span> Include your order number, the reason for the return, and photos of the item (if damaged or defective).</li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Return Authorization:</span> Our team will provide you with a <span class="boldpage">Return Authorization Number (RAN)</span> and detailed instructions on how to return the item.</li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Package the Item:</span> Carefully package the product in its original packaging to prevent damage during transit. The item must include all accessories, manuals, and warranties.</li>
    </ol>
<h3>3. Return Shipping Fees</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Free Return Shipping:</span>If the return is due to a defect, wrong item shipped, or damaged goods, we will provide a return shipping label at no cost. </li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Return Shipping Costs:</span> The customer is responsible for return shipping fees, unless the item was defective, or we made an error with the order.</li>
    </ul>
<h3>4. Restocking Fee</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Restocking Fee:</span>A <span class="boldpage">restocking fee of 3%</span> of the purchase price may apply to returned items that are in unused and resalable condition but are returned for reasons other than defects or errors on our part (e.g., incorrect order, buyer’s remorse). </li>
            <ul style="list-style-type:circle;">
                <li>This fee helps cover the cost of inspecting, repackaging, and restocking the returned product.</li>
                <li>The restocking fee will be <span class="boldpage">deducted from your refund.</span></li>
            </ul>
                <p><span class="boldpage">Example:</span> If you purchased an item for <span class="boldpage">₱5,000</span> and a <span class="boldpage">3% restocking fee</span> applies, your refund will be <span class="boldpage">₱4,850.</span></p>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Restocking Fee Exceptions:</span> No restocking fee will be charged if:</li>
        <ul style="list-style-type:circle;">
                <li>The product is defective.</li>
                <li>The wrong item was shipped.</li>
                <li>The product was damaged during shipping.</li>
                <li>The return is initiated due to an error on our part.</li>
            </ul>
    </ul>
<h3>5. Refund Process </h3>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Processing Time:</span> Once we receive the returned item and it meets our return policy conditions, we will process your refund within 7 business days from the date of receipt.</li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Refund Method:</span> Please note that it may take a few business days for the funds to appear in your account, depending on your payment provider.</li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Partial Refunds:</span> We reserve the right to issue partial refunds in cases where the returned item is missing parts, damaged, or shows signs of heavy use.</li>
    </ul>
<h3>6. Exchanges</h3>
<p>If you would like to exchange an item for a different model, color, or size, please contact our customer service team to initiate the exchange. The return process for exchanges is similar to the return process outlined above.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Exchange Eligibility: The item must be returned in unused, unopened, and resalable condition.</li>
        <li>Exchange Fees: Customers are responsible for any price differences, and shipping costs for exchanges.</li>
    </ul>
<h3>7. Defective or Damaged Items</h3>
<p>If you receive a damaged or defective gadget, please contact us immediately upon receiving your order. We will take the necessary steps to resolve the issue, which may include a repair, replacement, or refund.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Damaged Item:</span> Please provide photos or videos of the damaged product to help expedite the process.</li>
        <li><span class="boldpage">Defective Item:</span> If the item is found to be defective within 7 days of receiving it, we will offer a full refund, replacement, or repair, depending on stock availability and the nature of the defect.</li>
    </ul>
<h3>8. Items That Cannot Be Returned</h3>
<p>The following items are non-returnable and non-refundable:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Products that have been damaged due to misuse or mishandling</li>
        <li>Items with missing accessories, manuals, or parts</li>
        <li>Opened software, games, or electronics that are sealed</li>
        <li>Products bought on sale or discounted (unless defective)</li>
    </ul>
<h3>9. Changes to This Policy</h3>
</p><span class="boldpage">Allworld Corporation</span> reserves the right to modify or update this Return and Refund Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
